      Is sixty minutes worth watching?
      The storyline is really good and it's very action heavy. The fighting is a bit unrealistic but not enough to be weary about (since he's a mixed martial arts fighter) I really liked everything that was going on and the storyline is definitely really good compared to other foreign movies I've watched.
